pageContext.claim: “There has never been an administration -- and even some of our enemies are begrudgingly admitting this -- that has done what we've done in the first year and a half. Think of it.”
pageContext.analysis: This is not something you hear from Trump's real or perceived enemies. According to our Trump Promise Tracker, Trump has kept 23 percent of 60 key promises and broken 27 percent; many others remain unfulfilled.
